com.nkorasa.cmp.result

Class CmpPair<B,W>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nkorasa.cmp.result.CmpPair<B,W>
  • Type Parameters:
    B - base object generic type
    W - working object generic type

    public class CmpPair<B,W>
extends java.lang.Object
    Compare pair that represents compare result between base object from base collection and working object from working collection that are matched by the same key Key is provided with key Difference type is provided with diff If exists only in one collection and does not exist in another, it's value will be null. For example, all added items will be null in base collection, therefore base will be null
